{
    "description": "Push-up Phase 2: extend k=1 to k=2. 4 blocks, d=512, 8 heads, TNT chunkwise, dolmino_100b. Load 20K k=1 checkpoint, rewind cursor to step 15K position for 5K steps overlap before fresh data. 20K steps from step 15001. Matches proven formula: periodic reset, no m_norm clamp, GPT2 vocab.",
